         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">11/10/90 ¶  ¶ I should like to advise, respected Doctor, that  ¶ one ¶  decade of Australian Characeae be completed  ¶ by way of trial ¶  and published through your masterly treatment. ¶  Should time ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">90.10.11</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Nordstedt</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">11/10/90</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Möchte rathen, verehrter, Herr Doctor, dass </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">eine</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Decade australischer Characeen </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">versuchsweise</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> ausgearbeitet und veröffentlicht würde durch Ihre meisterhafte Behandlung. Sollte Ihnen dafür Zeit übrig sein, so möchte ich fragen, wieviel Kosten eine solche Decade verursachen würden, u wieviel die Subsidie für 100 Exemplare sein müsste. Wenn der Anfang gemacht sein wird, würde auch wohl an eine Weiterführung u Vollendung zu denken sein.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie ehrend der Ihre</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">11/10/90</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I should like to advise, respected Doctor, that <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">one</hi>
               </seg> decade of Australian <name key="Characeae">Characeae</name> be completed <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">by way of trial</hi>
               </seg> and published through your masterly treatment.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nordstedt (1891).</p>
               </note> Should time remain for you for it, I should like to ask how much cost such a decade would entail and how much the subsidy must be for 100 copies. When the beginning will be made, [I] would be thinking of a continuation and completion.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Characeae">Characeae</name>
            </p>
         </div>
